      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAYDEN'S FANCY (4) was quickly into stride and burnt early from out wide where he gave a sight, finishing second (20.84) and beaten 1.75 lengths over 365m at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Capable of going well again. TWISTED BOHDI (8) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 20.68 beating Beats Per Minute. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Leading chance again. EDDY SPAGHETTI (1) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at this track over 365m (20.98). Form here at the trip sound including two wins. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. EL CONDOR PASA (7) deserves plenty of thought over this trip.",
